data.purpose: To consider and approve the unaudited financial statements/results for the quarter and half year ended September 30, 2024 and amendment to the articles of association of the Company.

Update on Board Meeting dated August 17, 2024 - We write to inform that the Company is proposing to issue share warrants by way of preferential allotment to promoters and key managerial personnel and determination of issue price thereof as may be permitted under applicable laws
To consider the proposal for raising of funds by way of issue of one or more instruments/ securities and determination of issue price thereof
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended Jun 30, 2024
